    <comment>Update to 0.2.5: Lark grammar frontend; sparse FSM end states (removes quadratic FSM-construction memory); prevent XML whitespace state explosion; plus 0.2.4 fixes. Source now generated from the git tag via _service (upstream dropped the PyPI sdist; C++ build needs bundled 3rdparty submodules). %check smoke test temporarily tolerates the transformers ImportError caused by the current Factory python-transformers 5.14.1 (tokenizers&lt;=0.23.0) vs python-tokenizers 0.23.1 skew, while still asserting the native C++ binding loads.</comment>
